<BaseLayout title="About — Gobind Singh"><section class="container grid gap-12 py-20 lg:grid-cols-[.7fr_1.3fr] lg:py-32"><div><img src="/images/profile.jpg" alt="Gobind Singh" class="sticky top-28 aspect-[3/4] w-full rounded-2xl object-cover" /></div><div><PageHeader eyebrow="About" title="Curious, practical, and always learning." /><div class="prose"><p>I’m Gobind Singh, a Software Engineer at Google with a B.E. in Computer Science from BITS Pilani.</p><p>My interests sit at the intersection of machine learning, large language models, computer vision, distributed systems, systems engineering, healthcare AI, and product engineering.</p><p>I worked on ECG arrhythmia detection under Prof. Sumeet Sourav at CSIR-CEERI and have professional experience across Google and DeepTek AI.</p><p>Outside work, I care about basketball, reading, poetry, photography, weekend travel, and writing long-form technical articles.</p></div></div></section></BaseLayout>
